name: Login Profile
description:
As an employee of the company
I want to login my employee profile using my credentials
In order to collaborate with my colleagues

steps.name: I am on the "Company home" page on URL "www.mycomany.com"
I fill in "Username" with "Test"
I fill in "Password" with "123"
I click on the "Log In" button
I am on the "My profile" page on URL "www.mycompany.com/myprofile"
I should see "Welcome to your profile" message
I should see the "Log out" button
I click on the "Edit Personal Info" button
I fill in "Your name" with "Thilina Ashen Gamage"
I click on the "Save Changes" button
I should see "Your personal info has been successfully updated" message

arguments.val: Your personal info has been successfully updated
